    <div class="fail-block"><h3>SmartHQ Wi-Fi connection</h3><p>Wi-Fi config / app re-pair first. Module $260–$400 only if hardware-side confirmed.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Matte finish exterior damage</h3><p>Abrasive-cleaner damage common. Panel replacement 2-4 week lead. Quoted individually by finish.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Oven igniter glow-but-no-heat</h3><p>Igniter $220–$340 on Café gas-oven variants.</p></div>
